// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3895 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c4767ce2-a172-527a-b034-42b619521066

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
